comments.content:
The direct and indirect causal inputs upstream and downstream of Tyrobp in microglial cells.


Proteins on this pathway have targeted assays available via the [CPTAC Assay Portal](https://assays.cancer.gov/available_assays?wp_id=WP3945).
This pathway was inferred from Mus musculus pathway "TYROBP Causal Network", WP3625 revision 85694 with a 96.0% conversion rate.
